'''Antigonish Arena''' is a 2,290-seat multi-purpose [[arena]] in [[Antigonish, Nova Scotia]], [[Canada]]. It is home to both the [[Maritime Junior A Hockey League|Junior A]] and [[Nova Scotia Junior Hockey League|Junior B]] [[Antigonish Bulldogs]] [[ice hockey|hockey]] teams. The arena was home to the [[St. Francis Xavier X-Men]] and [[St. Francis Xavier X-Women|X-Women]] hockey teams before they moved into a new on-campus [[Charles V. Keating Millennium Centre|arena]]. 
